com.facebook.buck.parser

Class DefaultParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.parser.DefaultParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parser

    public class DefaultParser
extends Object
implements Parser
    Evaluates build files using one of the supported interpreters and provides information about build targets defined in them.

    Computed targets are cached but are automatically invalidated if Watchman reports any filesystem changes that may affect computed results.
